      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly in absolutely pristine condition! It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered like one of the family, and still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look and fall in love! \u2728",
