    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an immaculate E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet following a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement. Underneath, the chassis is flawless with a reinforced rear subframe ensuring optimal torsional rigidity. Factory-spec bushings and an M-Variable differential maintain the razor-sharp handling characteristics this chassis is known for. The exterior retains a deep, showroom luster with zero oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
