      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous collector. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and recent preventative maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved masterpiece that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 46500.0,
